cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper proposes a high-speed online neural network classifier based on extreme learning machines for multi-label classification. This work involves machine learning techniques and deals with classification problems in various domains such as multimedia, text, and biology. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves image processing (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), and multimedia (cs.MM) domains. The proposed method also involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Hence, these sub-categories are also likely.
